&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ocm sign component-version</title><link>https://ocm.software/docs/reference/ocm-cli/ocm-sign-component-version/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ocm.software/docs/reference/ocm-cli/ocm-sign-component-version/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="ocm-sign-component-version"&gt;ocm sign component-version&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sign component version(s) inside an OCM repository&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Creates or update cryptographic signatures on component descriptors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="reference-format"&gt;Reference Format&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;[type::]{repository}/[valid-prefix]/{component}[:version]
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prefixes: {component-descriptors|none} (default: &amp;ldquo;component-descriptors&amp;rdquo;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repo types: {OCIRepository|CommonTransportFormat} (short: {OCI|oci|CTF|ctf})&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="ocm-signing-explained-in-simple-steps"&gt;OCM Signing explained in simple steps&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resolve OCM repository&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fetch component version&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify digests (&amp;ndash;verify-digest-consistency)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Normalise descriptor (&amp;ndash;normalisation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hash normalised descriptor (&amp;ndash;hash)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sign hash (&amp;ndash;signer-spec)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="behavior"&gt;Behavior&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conflicting signatures cause failure unless &amp;ndash;force is set (then overwrite)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;ndash;dry-run: compute only, do not persist signature&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Default signature name: default&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Default signer: RSASSA-PSS plugin (needs private key)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use this command to establish provenance of component versions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>ocm sign</title><link>https://ocm.software/docs/reference/ocm-cli/ocm-sign/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ocm.software/docs/reference/ocm-cli/ocm-sign/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="ocm-sign"&gt;ocm sign&lt;/h2&gt;
